   "0.521865889212828`", 
   "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\" km\\\\[ThreeSuperior]\"\>"}],
  SequenceForm[
  "Volume of voxels: ", 0.521865889212828, " km\\[ThreeSuperior]"],
